sectionsArray.md:
Average (Mean) = \frac{\text{Sum of all data points}}{\text{Number of data points}}
- Sum of all data points: Add all the values together.
- Number of data points: Count of values in the data set.
Range = \text{Largest value} - \text{Smallest value}
- Largest value: The highest number in the data set.
- Smallest value: The lowest number in the data set.

